Connect to an MCP (Model Context Protocol) server at runtime to discover and use its tools. Use this when you need to interact with an external service that exposes an MCP endpoint. Only streamable HTTP (http/https) URLs are supported. After connecting, the server's tools become available for the rest of this session. The server_id you provide will prefix all discovered tool names (e.g. server_id "weather" + tool "forecast" = "weather_forecast").